platform.tilera

Class ParseExecutionLog

  • java.lang.Object
    • platform.tilera.ParseExecutionLog

  • public class ParseExecutionLog
extends java.lang.Object
    Parse the execution log generated by the framework running on Tilera platform. This is an example of a hardware log file *** Start *** Proc Id : 0 CPU Grid (0, 0) 0 Proc Id : 3 CPU Grid (3, 0) 3 Proc Id : 2 CPU Grid (2, 0) 2 Proc Id : 1 CPU Grid (1, 0) 1 0, 22495687404374461, 22495687404664645, 22495687404409817, 22495687404656400, 22495687404401126, 22495687404651377, 22495687404411696, 22495687404644403, 1, 22495687404778560, 22495687404999386, 22495687404784604, 22495687404988349, 22495687404779792, 22495687404983107, 22495687404765222, 22495687404986552, .... 99, 22495687434776102, 22495687435010964, 22495687434782165, 22495687434999317, 22495687434793363, 22495687434994309, 22495687434769638, 22495687434998148, *** Finished ***
    Author:
    Pranav Tendulkar
